<h3>Why Rwanda?</h3>
<p>Mario traveled widely, and his favorite place in the world was the mountains of Rwanda. We can't sell coffee that grown near our homes, but whenever we can, we like to feature Rwandan beans. That country is close to our hearts, just like it was for Uncle Mario. </p>
